org.foxlabs.validation.constraint

Annotation Type SupportedLocale


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={ANNOTATION_TYPE,METHOD,FIELD})
public @interface SupportedLocale
    Checks whether the annotated locale is in list of available locales supported by JRE.
    Author:
    Fox Mulder
    See Also:
    SupportedLocaleConstraint

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String[] groups

    • Element Detail

      • message

        public abstract String message
        Returns:
        Overriding error message template. Empty string means that default message template should be used.
        Default:
        ""

      • groups

        public abstract String[] groups
        Returns:
        Array of groups the constraint is applied on. Empty array means default group.
        Default:
        {}

      • targets

        public abstract ValidationTarget[] targets
        Returns:
        An object part to which constraint should be applied. ValidationTarget.VALUE will be used by default.
        Default:
        {}
